data.description: Step into a time capsule of history and grace, where vintage Southern charm meets unlimited possibilities for modern comfort. This home is in the heart of a charming town square & offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a delightful wrap-around porch. Immerse yourself in the nostalgia of a bygone era while enjoying the opportunity to design the home to meet your own style of living. The best part, it is a blank canvas on the inside! Sheetrock is in place and this is an investor DREAM! Home flooded in Florence and has been gutted and rebuilt since Don't miss the opportunity to make this captivating residence your forever home.
